00:33:06.391 --> 00:33:08.408
# Love and happiness #

641
00:33:08.410 --> 00:33:10.310
Christmas is...

642
00:33:10.312 --> 00:33:13.713
joy, family...

643
00:33:13.715 --> 00:33:15.348
Okay.

644
00:33:17.419 --> 00:33:18.785
Deuces.

645
00:33:22.691 --> 00:33:24.791
Are you kidding me?

646
00:33:31.333 --> 00:33:32.499
Mm.

647
00:33:32.501 --> 00:33:33.566
Hey...

648
00:33:34.636 --> 00:33:36.836
that was pretty intense.

649
00:33:36.838 --> 00:33:39.506
Never met someone
so anti-Santa before.


650
00:33:39.508 --> 00:33:40.573
Nah, I love Santa.

651
00:33:40.575 --> 00:33:42.575
He... He roasted me last week,

652
00:33:42.577 --> 00:33:44.844
so I had to hit him back.
You know what I mean?


653
00:33:44.846 --> 00:33:47.380
So are you
the, uh, entitled rich girl?


654
00:33:47.382 --> 00:33:49.382
Excuse me?

655
00:33:49.384 --> 00:33:51.551
I-I'm supposed to let you
stew in your own guilt,


656
00:33:51.553 --> 00:33:53.453
and then you get all scared
with anticipation,


657
00:33:53.455 --> 00:33:56.589
but, uh,
it's not really my style.


658
00:33:56.591 --> 00:33:58.725
You know what? I'm good.

659
00:33:58.727 --> 00:34:00.460
Hold on, Second Chance.

660
00:34:00.462 --> 00:34:01.561
Don't touch me!

661
00:34:02.731 --> 00:34:04.464
I got a job to do,

662
00:34:04.466 --> 00:34:06.800
and your leaving wouldn't
allow me to accomplish that,


663
00:34:06.802 --> 00:34:09.336
so why don't you
do us both a favor


664
00:34:09.338 --> 00:34:12.339
and just drop the
"I'm better than everyone" act?


665
00:34:12.341 --> 00:34:13.940
Okay, look. I don't know
what you're getting at,


666
00:34:13.942 --> 00:34:15.608
but I don't even know you!

667
00:34:15.610 --> 00:34:17.410
Well, I know you.

668
00:34:18.413 --> 00:34:20.163
Fifth grade,
you stole a candy bar.


669
00:34:20.164 --> 00:34:21.914
Sixth grade, put gum
in Cindy Fletcher's hair


670
00:34:21.917 --> 00:34:24.551
at recess and blamed it
on Frankie Fletcher.


671
00:34:24.553 --> 00:34:27.354
Oh, same here.
Cheated on a test.


672
00:34:27.356 --> 00:34:28.755
Then eighth grade...Hoo!

673
00:34:28.757 --> 00:34:30.757
Okay, okay, I get it.

674
00:34:30.759 --> 00:34:34.928
You're a stalker,
a really committed one.


675
00:34:34.930 --> 00:34:36.529
Super impressive, really.

676
00:34:42.571 --> 00:34:44.037
I'm a ghost.
You got that part, right?


677
00:34:45.507 --> 00:34:47.474
If you run, I'll catch you.

678
00:34:47.476 --> 00:34:49.509
If you hide, I'll find you.

679
00:34:49.511 --> 00:34:51.878
Think of me like you
would think of a cold.


680
00:34:51.880 --> 00:34:54.848
You got me.
I'm gonna be here for a while.


681
00:34:54.850 --> 00:34:56.683
You gotta put up with me.

682
00:34:56.685 --> 00:34:58.551
Then I'll be gone.

683
00:34:58.553 --> 00:35:00.420
You want me
to think of you like a cold?


684
00:35:00.422 --> 00:35:01.688
That's the best
you can come up with?


685
00:35:01.690 --> 00:35:03.523
I'm thinking on the fly here.

686
00:35:03.525 --> 00:35:04.824
Look, shut up, and let's ride.

687
00:35:12.701 --> 00:35:13.733
We didn't go anywhere.

688
00:35:13.735 --> 00:35:15.402
You gotta move your feet.

689
00:35:15.404 --> 00:35:16.603
If you wanna go somewhere,

690
00:35:16.605 --> 00:35:17.937
I'm parked out front.

691
00:35:19.641 --> 00:35:21.074
Fine.

692
00:35:26.548 --> 00:35:29.849
Okay. So you have
some type of ghost magic


693
00:35:29.851 --> 00:35:32.886
where you can transport,
but we're in your car?


694
00:35:32.888 --> 00:35:34.854
I like driving.

695
00:35:34.856 --> 00:35:36.923
Well, at least
my dreams are creative.


696
00:35:36.925 --> 00:35:38.958
Baby, I'm the Ghost
of Christmas Present.


697
00:35:38.960 --> 00:35:40.927
You're the Ghost
of Christmas Presents?


698
00:35:40.929 --> 00:35:42.629
Present.

699
00:35:43.565 --> 00:35:45.632
- Present!
- Oh.


700
00:35:45.634 --> 00:35:47.567
Guess you're awake now, huh?

701
00:35:47.569 --> 00:35:49.969
Now get on board
with the process.


702
00:36:03.618 --> 00:36:05.885
Okay, okay.

703
00:36:05.887 --> 00:36:07.987
I'm having a nervous breakdown.

704
00:36:07.989 --> 00:36:09.556
Wonderful.

705
00:36:10.625 --> 00:36:12.725
So, where are we going?

706
00:36:12.727 --> 00:36:14.127
Almost there.

707
00:36:15.630 --> 00:36:17.313
Where's there?

708
00:36:17.314 --> 00:36:18.997
Well, you never gave him
a housewarming gift,


709
00:36:19.000 --> 00:36:20.667
and you never, ever
let your driver


710
00:36:20.669 --> 00:36:21.768
drop him off first.

711
00:36:21.770 --> 00:36:23.286
Look,

712
00:36:23.287 --> 00:36:24.803
can we just be done
with all of this?


713
00:36:24.806 --> 00:36:27.540
Oh, I can maybe give you
something that you want,


714
00:36:27.542 --> 00:36:29.809
and you could tell your boss
or whoever's in charge


715
00:36:29.811 --> 00:36:31.744
that you got the job done?

716
00:36:31.746 --> 00:36:33.480
Are you trying to bribe me?

717
00:36:33.482 --> 00:36:34.681
Well...

718
00:36:34.683 --> 00:36:35.882
Girl, please!

719
00:36:36.885 --> 00:36:38.585
Your assistant
has nothing in here


720
00:36:38.587 --> 00:36:40.887
but condiments and pickles.
Are pickles a condiment?


721
00:36:40.889 --> 00:36:43.056
What are we doing
in my assistant's kitchen?


722
00:36:43.058 --> 00:36:44.624
Your choices, boo.

723
00:36:44.626 --> 00:36:46.092
My choices?

724
00:36:46.094 --> 00:36:47.660
Let's have a look.

725
00:36:58.740 --> 00:37:00.039
Hey, Dad.

726
00:37:00.041 --> 00:37:01.808
How you guys holding up?

727
00:37:01.810 --> 00:37:05.578
Hey, champ. We're doing okay.

728
00:37:05.580 --> 00:37:07.180
Did you get that girl
to marry you yet?


729
00:37:10.819 --> 00:37:12.519
Oh, I don't know. Not yet.

730
00:37:12.521 --> 00:37:15.655
Uh, she's, you know, busy.

731
00:37:15.657 --> 00:37:17.056
He has a girlfriend?

732
00:37:17.058 --> 00:37:18.124
Nope.

733
00:37:21.796 --> 00:37:22.929
Uh...

734
00:37:22.931 --> 00:37:26.900
my cards are maxed out.

735
00:37:26.902 --> 00:37:29.936
Did you send the transfer
for the week?


736
00:37:29.938 --> 00:37:31.871
Yeah, I
-I just sent it.

737
00:37:33.608 --> 00:37:34.607
Is that Brian?

738
00:37:34.609 --> 00:37:36.009
Oh, hey.

739
00:37:36.011 --> 00:37:37.043
Come on.

740
00:37:37.045 --> 00:37:38.678
Look who's awake!

741
00:37:38.680 --> 00:37:39.679
Hey.

742
00:37:39.681 --> 00:37:40.680
There she is!

743
00:37:40.682 --> 00:37:41.915
How you doing, beautiful?

744
00:37:41.917 --> 00:37:42.949
How they treating you?

745
00:37:42.951 --> 00:37:45.818
Um, not too bad.

746
00:37:45.820 --> 00:37:48.021
Oh, I'll be dancing
out of here tomorrow.


747
00:37:50.625 --> 00:37:53.927
How are you, Brian?
How's your week been?


748
00:37:53.929 --> 00:37:57.730
Aw, my day was good,
and I'm fine, Mama.


749
00:37:57.732 --> 00:38:00.633
I just wish I was
right there, right next to you.


750
00:38:00.635 --> 00:38:02.101
I'm sorry I'm not.

751
00:38:02.103 --> 00:38:04.904
Don't you worry yourself,
sweetheart.


752
00:38:04.906 --> 00:38:06.739
We understand.

753
00:38:06.741 --> 00:38:08.908
We'll spend Christmas
together next year.


754
00:38:09.844 --> 00:38:11.578
We are so proud of you.

755
00:38:11.580 --> 00:38:12.579
Yeah.

756
00:38:13.648 --> 00:38:15.114
Thank you, Mom.

757
00:38:16.751 --> 00:38:18.184
Oh. Uh, feeling...

758
00:38:18.186 --> 00:38:20.153
No, i-it's all right,

759
00:38:20.155 --> 00:38:21.721
It's okay. It's okay.

760
00:38:21.723 --> 00:38:23.690
- Just hold on.
- Hey, what's going on?


761
00:38:23.692 --> 00:38:24.691
I'll get somebody.

762
00:38:24.693 --> 00:38:27.026
Is Mom all right? Mom!

763
00:38:29.064 --> 00:38:30.997
Sh
-She's okay.

764
00:38:30.999 --> 00:38:33.733
Uh, the I.V. just popped out.

765
00:38:36.171 --> 00:38:37.804
Okay. All right.

766
00:38:38.807 --> 00:38:41.674
Just a second, pal.

767
00:38:41.676 --> 00:38:42.675
Nurse?

768
00:39:02.731 --> 00:39:05.665
Your choices
have consequences.


769
00:39:05.667 --> 00:39:07.934
My choices?

770
00:39:07.936 --> 00:39:10.236
